events.name: Awareness Campaign

venue.name: Telnet Technologies
venue.address_1: B-2, Mahaveer Colony, Ratanada
venue.address_2: Near Bhaskar Circle, Opp. Mangal-deep Apartment

events.description:
This is women exclusive event and gentlemen are also invited.
As you may know, to showcase latest state of art technologies, Google Developers Group Jodhpur (GDGJodhpur) is a non profit community in Jodhpur. Along with DevFest18 we are looking to motivate innovative and problem solving project ideas that can provide a premium experience to technical enthusiasts.
Recently Google has also announced exciting contest for Science project by school students under class-wise categories. The initiative is designed to help and motivate innovative & artistic efforts by various school students. We believe that on the road of fast pacing technology, Science teachers from various schools must be invited for an awareness camp that will convey them about the available opportunities for students. The bulk of our agenda is devoted to provide quality resources that will support project ideas to students through teachers in well guided mode. We are striving to provide an open, free and quality platform where teachers can update themselves with the wealth of latest announcements along with experts & like minded people. We are the first technical community in the state of Rajasthan who has been actively enduring the odds with a passionate team of technocrates.

This is direct invitation for teachers to join our free awareness camp regarding available opportunities.

events.name: [Online] Levelling up as Developer
events.description:
[Online Event] IN Collaboration with GDG Ahmedabad

Never feel you are the best till you Meet Mr. Romin Irani, he would provide you insight into what it takes and means to be best in the software development industry as he is one of them

In continuation of our Saga of enlightening and encouraging today's top tech brains, we bring to you
a former GDE, a Googler and The Ultimate Mr. Romin Irani.

He is available over:
- https://rominirani.com/
- https://twitter.com/iRomin
Youtube Stream URL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F8nEMtGCtYw

Abstract:
If you think that learning new technologies/frameworks is enough to take your development career to the next level, you are likely missing out on creating a wider impact both from a personal and professional career level. Learn how you can take your development journey to the next level via a set of tips and experiences that will be shared during the session.

About Speaker:
Romin Irani works at Google, specifically on Google Cloud Platform. 25 years experienced young developer exploring the horizon of Software industry, passionate about helping developers succeed. More on his blog https://rominirani.com/ and You may follow him on https://twitter.com/iRomin
